<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4f33d1f0f415906a1e482b5334fe9c7b>.
<#4f33d1f0f415906a1e482b5334fe9c7b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/0757b95c-829b-43da-8864-6cee947c93ce>;
