<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#1760496ebc23fe6ee6c7ee3b47d2de2a>.
<#1760496ebc23fe6ee6c7ee3b47d2de2a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
