    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-14T07:01:21.788Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#f0d2c9be843115786ed2737fc0bc8e00> {
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/ee32d342-c9bd-41ae-8eb7-75b9307cf491> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Öppna data"@sv, "Inspire"@sv, "Hydrografi"@sv, "Hydrologi"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
