    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/22f4326a-afe1-410c-9325-8468bbe0f453> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <urn:uuid:838ea933-75b4-eddc-a685-121f714ea9f0>;
