<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#49699ebb285fdf40af588c72db7c552b>.
<#49699ebb285fdf40af588c72db7c552b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://www.geodata.se/resources/7108499d-23de-4d05-baa4-e45020d32bcc>;
