    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#165d5f1bb9143e410e8aa0e9b0204194>.
<#165d5f1bb9143e410e8aa0e9b0204194> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
